## 7. مخطط قاعدة البيانات الجديد (المُغيَّر فقط)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    AspNetUsers ||--o| Donor : "UserId (string)"
    Donor ||--o{ DonorMedicalDocument : "DonorID"
    Donor {
        int DonorID
        string UserId FK
        DonorApprovalStatus ApprovalStatus
        string RejectionReason
        DateTime ApprovalDate
        string ReviewedByUserId
    }
    DonorMedicalDocument {
        int DocumentID
        int DonorID FK
        string DocumentType
        string FilePath
        DateTime UploadedAt
        bool IsVerified
    }
    Donation {
        int DonationID
        TestResult TestResult
        DateTime TestedAt
        string TestedByUserId
        bool IsAddedToInventory
    }
    BloodRequest {
        int RequestID
        int QuantityNeeded
        int QuantityFulfilled
        RequestStatus Status
    }
    BloodInventoryItem {
        int InventoryItemID
        DateTime ExpiryDate
        BloodUnitStatus Status
    }
```

